{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e7057a47b1","title":"行军中严格注意隐藏","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"95d0ea9b10","index":0,"year":1936,"month":2,"day":16,"articleId":"e7057a47b1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"54042453fc","type":"paragraph","text":"行军中严格注意隐藏","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"e7057a47b1"},{"id":"a7b8a863eb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年2月16日）爱、程：甲、隐蔽运动，避敌发现，为争取胜利之严重条件。各兵团应遵照达次命令，于敌机活动时间停止运动，派出主官首长指挥，绕过暴露地段及集中地。如不严格隐蔽，因而暴露企图，将唯各兵团首长是问。杰村。乙、子华即令延水之水手，荣臻即令在双庙河之水手开来高丙、此电由子华派人交叶参谋长巴。选次令交叶之电报均送交否？即复。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"e7057a47b1"},{"id":"14ce1398cf","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"e7057a47b1"},{"id":"5250dfdc18","type":"paragraph","text":"十六号二十三时半[1]这是毛泽东和红军第一方面军司令员彭德怀给第一方面平第一军团政治委员蛋荣臻、第十五军团政治委员程子华的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"e7057a47b1"}],"page":{"id":"9373defbe7","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"e7057a47b1","start":233,"end":233}}}},"__N_SSG":true}